│ assertion.\n\n4. Proposed Edit Point(s):\nEdit Local.cpp in              │
│ removeUnwindEdge to avoid calling getCleanupPad() if operand 0 is no     │
│ longer a CleanupPadInst. Instead, use the raw operand, which can be      │
